      <h1 class="content-hero-title">Psychedelic Law</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">Psychedelic law is changing faster than at any point since the 1960s — but unevenly, and with significant complexity. This page covers the legal landscape in Canada and internationally, explains the critical distinctions between decriminalisation and legalisation, and outlines what current access pathways actually mean in practice.</p>
